WEBVTT

00:00.042 --> 00:02.330
<i>Previously on "Once Upon a Time"...</i>

00:02.336 --> 00:03.535
You killed my father!

00:03.637 --> 00:05.404
I merely <i>ordered</i> him killed.

00:05.841 --> 00:07.674
Dead men tell no tales.

00:08.845 --> 00:10.778
[Groans]

00:11.136 --> 00:14.338
Emma Swan, will you marry me?

00:14.440 --> 00:16.206
Yes!

00:16.475 --> 00:18.642
This is your chance
at love and happiness.

00:18.744 --> 00:19.977
That's him?

00:19.983 --> 00:21.382
Go get him.

00:21.580 --> 00:23.714
[Indistinct conversations]

00:25.251 --> 00:27.818
[Groans, screams]

00:32.223 --> 00:34.291
Aah!

00:34.393 --> 00:35.993
Ahh.

00:36.095 --> 00:37.828
Hope that didn't sting.

